OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FIt's a Friday morning and Doncaster MP
OL,7,FLee Pitcher is holding his
OL,8,Fconstituency surgery, where the people
OL,9,Fhe represents get the chance to talk
OL,10,Fto him face-to-face about their
OL,11,Fconcerns.
OL,13,FInside the room he and his
OL,14,Fconstituents discuss the issues
OL,15,Fthey've raised, but outside a security
OL,16,Fguard stands watch.
OL,18,FIt is an insight into the daily lives
OL,19,Fof politicians - the constant concerns
OL,20,Fabout safety that have become just
OL,21,Fpart of the routine.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
