PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781878275
OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FMr Pitcher says he is "hugely
OL,7,Fconscious, almost obsessively" about
OL,8,Fsecurity.
OL,10,F"It's not just my own safety that I'm
OL,11,Fthinking about, I'm thinking about my
OL,12,Fteam and of course my family who feel
OL,13,Fevery single thing that ever happens
OL,14,Fto me" he tells me," he tells me.
OL,16,FAt his home, panic alarms have been
OL,17,Finstalled in case of emergencies, but
OL,18,Fthat doesn't stop the worry.
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@^O]rD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
