CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781878275
OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FRecently a window smashed in his
OL,7,Fkitchen. He doesn't know what
OL,8,Fhappened, but says it looked like a
OL,9,F"rifle shot".
OL,11,FEven if it was innocuous, it brought
OL,12,Finto focus some of the risks
OL,13,Fpoliticians face.
OL,15,FMr Pitcher says: "That first night
OL,16,Fwhen you go to bed after something
OL,17,Flike that happens, it is really hard
OL,18,Fto sleep because you just never know."
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@ROU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
