OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FOver the past couple of months, I've
OL,7,Fbeen talking to politicians of all
OL,8,Fstripes about some of the threats they
OL,9,Fface 10 years since Jo Cox's murder.
OL,11,FThere is a wide consensus that, while
OL,12,Fsome of the security measures have
OL,13,Fimproved, the toxicity of our politics
OL,14,Fhas also meant the abuse and
OL,15,Fintimidation has worsened.
OL,17,FIn a survey for the Speaker's
OL,18,FConference published last year, only
OL,19,Faround half of MPs said they feel safe
OL,20,Fin their job.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
