CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781878275
OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FMeanwhile, 96% said they had
OL,7,Fexperienced one or more incidents of
OL,8,Fthreatening behaviour or communication.
OL,10,FAnd this is an issue that crosses
OL,11,Fparty lines.
OL,13,FI brought together a Labour MP,
OL,14,FShipley's Anna Dixon, and a
OL,15,FConservative MP, Alicia Kearns from
OL,16,FRutland and Stamford, both of whom
OL,17,Fshared grim stories of the death
OL,18,Fthreats they had faced.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
