CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781878275
OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FMs Dixon only became an MP two years
OL,7,Fago. She says she has been "shocked"
OL,8,Fby the level of abuse politicians face.
OL,10,F"I've already had two online death
OL,11,Fthreats in addition to lots of other
OL,12,Ftypes of abuse," she said.
OL,14,FMs Kearns doesn't believe the
OL,15,Fsituation has improved in the last
OL,16,Fdecade and gets upset as she recalls
OL,17,Fhow fellow Conservative MP and "good
OL,18,Ffriend" David Amess was murdered in
OL,19,F2021.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781878275
OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,F"People demonise us and don't see us
OL,7,Fas human," she says.
OL,9,F"And I spend a lot of my time working
OL,10,Fhard to show that I'm just a normal
OL,11,Fperson."
OL,13,FAmong the threats she received was one
OL,14,Ffrom a single mother in her
OL,15,Fconstituency, who made comments about
OL,16,Fher children.
OL,18,F"When the police went round and
OL,19,Fknocked on her door...she was like 'I
OL,20,Fwas drunk and I was angry'," Ms Kearns
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
