FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781878275
OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,F"I would never think to threaten a
OL,7,Fchild if I was angry."
OL,9,FMs Dixon adds: "The reality is that
OL,10,Fwe're out and about, we're
OL,11,Frecognisable, and people want to
OL,12,Fapproach, usually, to say, 'thank you,
OL,13,Fyou're doing a great job', but my
OL,14,Fimmediate reaction is to take a step
OL,15,Fback. There's that moment where you're
OL,16,Fgoing, 'friend or foe?'."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781878275
OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FShe says she is "on guard all the
OL,7,Ftime" and that she often chose "not to
OL,8,Fgo out to a pub or a restaurant with
OL,9,Ffamily and rather just meet people in
OL,10,Fa home because I know I can relax".
OL,12,FThe Speaker of the House of Commons,
OL,13,FSir Lindsay Hoyle, still remembers
OL,14,Fwhen he was informed Jo Cox had died.
OL,16,FHe told me: "I couldn't believe it...
OL,17,FI couldn't
OL,19,Ftake it in, I couldn't absorb what
OL,20,Fthey were telling me" before adding
OL,21,Fthat Jo Cox was "an inspiration".
OL,26,@nD@QOUoD@EO]oD@`OUrD@bO]xD@MOU|D@UO]}D@
OL,26,AQOU}D@`O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
