OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FThe security of politicians and those
OL,7,Faround them is the "one thing that
OL,8,Fkeeps me awake at night", Sir Lindsay
OL,9,Ftold me.
OL,11,F"We're learning all the time, we're
OL,12,Falways looking for new solutions" he
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FMPs want to be accessible and speaking
OL,16,Fto the people they represent is a key
OL,17,Fpart of their job.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@XO]sD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
