PN,33611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781878275
OL,3,CDeath threats and security guards:
OL,4,CReality of life as an MP
OL,6,FBut that comes with significant risks
OL,7,Fand what's depressingly clear, a
OL,8,Fdecade on from Jo Cox's murder, is
OL,9,Fthat many politicians feel the job
OL,10,Fthey do is putting them in danger.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
